name: Swamp Escape
description:

https://civitai.com/models/18734/mmtrs-test

There are many other great photorealistic models available at the moment, so there may not be a demand for this model now, but please use it if you like.

The difference between the standard and PLUS versions is slight, but you can use whichever you prefer... By the way, I like the standard and don't use the PLUS version.
